        <item>
          <title>Florida State's Norvell agrees to restructured contract that gives $4.5M to fundraising campaign</title>
          <description><![CDATA[TALLAHASSEE, Fla. (AP) — Florida State and Mike Norvell have agreed to a restructured contract that includes the football coach contributing $4.5 million of his 2025 salary to help launch a fundraising campaign amid the sport's changing financial landscape.]]></description>
